<div id="about">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="small-8 small-centered medium-uncentered medium-4 columns about">
			<%= image_tag('profile_picture.png', id: "profile_picture", alt: 'Ryan O\'Connor') %>
		</div>

		<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
			<div class="medium-pull-3 columns">
				<h2 id="about_header" class="about text-center">About Me</h2>
			</div>

			<p class="about_text">
				Hi, my name is Ryan O'Connor and I have just completed my 3rd year of software engineering at the University of Ottawa. I was first introduced to coding during my Visual Basic programming class back in high school. Ever since then I haven't looked back. After discovering how rewarding it is to solve a problem using code, I knew what I wanted to pursue as a career.
			</p>
			<p class="about_text">
				Currently I am the VP Academic of the <%= link_to "Software Engineering Student Association", "http://uottawa-sesa.ca" %> where I help organize weekly Ruby on Rails tutorials, study sessions, and monthly coding events for students. When I'm taking a break from coding and helping others, I like to go skating, snowmobiling, or enjoying my time out on the water.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="education">
	<div class="subtitle">
