		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
			<h3 class="subheaders">University of Ottawa</h3>
			<p class="date">September 2012 - Current</p>
		</div>

		<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
			<strong>BASc in Software Engineering</strong>
			<p>
				My studies at the University of Ottawa have allowed me to develop strong design skills by using requirements engineering techniques, analysis level diagrams, and design level diagrams. I've also learned how to translate requirements and diagrams into quality software. Java has been used as the main programming language for learning, however I've also had the opportunity to use HTML, CSS, SQL, and Ruby.
			</p>
