			<h2 class="text-center">Experience</h2>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
			<h3 class="subheaders">Bell Canada</h3>
			<p class="date">June 2014 - August 2014</p>
		</div>

		<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
			<strong>VoIP Manager - Service Assurance and Development</strong>
			<p>
				At Bell Canada I provided quality assurance for Bell's VoIP platform. I aided customers with validation testing and verified that their results were as expected by analyzing SIP traces using Wireshark. I was also part of testing for new version releases and helped with diagnosing system failures. During my time working at Bell Canada I implemented a call forwarding feature on FreeSwitch for internal release testing.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row paragraph">
		<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
			<h3 class="subheaders">SigmaPoint Technologies</h3>
			<p class="date">May 2013 - August 2013</p>
		</div>

		<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
			<strong>Kontron Mechanic</strong>
			<p>
				SigmaPoint Technologies is an electronics manufacturer, where I worked as a Kontron mechanic. I assembled, diagnosed, and repaired CompactPCI boards and server boards. I worked under the Toyota Production System, used to provide quality products in a fast and efficient manner all while reducing waste.
			</p>
